name: Wednesday Addams - Jenna Ortega (Netflix Series)
description:
I made a Textual Inversion of Wednesday Addams from the Netflix Series.

2 Versions with base Checkpoints 1.4 and 1.5
(with Variations Strong and Light)

1.4 TIs mostly gives clearer results

You could take your prefered TI and rename it without the endings "w3day_14" to "w3day" or something else, Trigger word depends on Filename.

TI at the beginning of the Prompt may override described Styles which aiming not on photorealistic, use the keyword at the end or use the light version if the embedding is to strong.
